This research integrates social network analysis and bibliometric keyword analysis to draw a picture for the development of science, which can be called a "Science map". Hence each country, research institution, or researcher that contributes to the literature can be positioned. Processes for this research method are: 1) literature retrieval and filtering; 2) keyword revision and standardization; 3) visualization of three-dimensional network; 4) network properties calculation; and 5) visualization of two-dimensional knowledge map. 


